(text "== Two rear USB-C data/charging ports: J21 left and J11 right ==" (at 20.32 12.7 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 350a3986-1d35-5ca2-8a33-e9bef4f7f7c0))
(text "Both ports carry USB 3.2 Gen 2 plus USB2 and can sink negotiated 15V or source protected default USB current." (at 20.32 20.32 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid a4ca6be5-af4b-51f3-8168-eb0afce00765))
(text "TPS25751A loads a versioned 32KB EEPROM image while powered from dead-battery VBUS; no EC is needed to obtain the first 15V contract." (at 20.32 27.94 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid a5577deb-95b0-5849-9c8c-db49afb856dc))
(text "The raw 5V attach rail stays below the Type-C pre-attach capacitance limit; large sink bulk is behind the integrated PD switch." (at 20.32 35.56 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid d84e5f54-f678-5404-aae9-5dcfcbf1426a))
(text "== J21: USB 3.2 Gen 2 data plus USB-PD charging, side port 1 ==" (at 20.32 50.8 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 2951f5b3-6127-5420-8266-a74c026e31a2))
