(text "The EC reads each TPS25751A contract first, programs the BQ25798 input limit, then enables exactly one default-off TPS26630 path." (at 20.32 670.56 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 3a3efb9e-3117-5c8c-a88c-cff1efb4bc65))
(text "LTC4418 independently validates approximately 13.1V to 17.1V and prevents either attached adapter from backfeeding the other." (at 20.32 678.18 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 881a0081-43d5-513c-badf-0adf2a6c31ca))
(text "Five-port source budget: 5 x 0.9A maximum advertised load = 4.5A on the dedicated 6A USB_PORT_5V rail." (at 20.32 693.42 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 069e3732-60c4-55dd-a95d-39fcebee3e4a))
(text "Firmware must reject any configuration that advertises more than default USB current and must shed optional ports on rail fault." (at 20.32 701.04 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid ededd26c-04b3-5c9f-91d3-5c50508fbb7a))
